BLUEJAY

INFLUENCER PROGRAM TEMPLATE

The Bluejay Influencer Program Template is the ultimate solution for businesses looking to optimize their influencer referral program. This template offers a wide range of features designed to help your influencers promote your brand and drive more referrals.

The Bluejay Influencer Program Template is built with cutting-edge web development technologies, including Bootstrap 4 Framework, HTML5, CSS3, and JQuery. It is fully responsive and compatible with all devices and browsers, providing a seamless user experience.

The Bluejay template supports multiple payment options, including PayPal, gift cards, and vouchers, and is available in 20 languages.
TRY IT FREE
LIVE PREVIEW
This template offers a simple and efficient registration process for your influencers. They can register through traditional registration and login forms, or use a one-click access link. Businesses can also customize the registration form to collect additional information from advocates.

With the Bluejay Template's 15 sharing channels, your influencers can easily be brand advocates. This influencer program template provides a range of popular referral channels, including the referral link, email widget, WhatsApp, Instagram, Tiktok, Facebook, and Twitter. These tools help your influencers easily share your products and services with their network, boosting engagement and driving more referrals to your business.

The Bluejay Template's influencer stats section allows influencers to track their referral performance and focus on the advocacy tools that work best. This feature allows influencers to quickly review their total referrals and rewards, view their referral history, track bonuses, and see the status of their referrals.

EASY AND ATTRACTIVE INFLUENCER PAYMENT OPTIONS

The Bluejay Template makes it easy for influencers to get rewarded with multiple payment options available, including prepaid gift cards, bank transfers, and PayPal cash. These payment methods provide attractive options for building an influencer program that motivates your influencers to refer qualified candidates.
